| **No input validation** | Added parameter validation and type checking |
| **Missing error handling** | Added try-catch blocks and global error handler |
| **Information leakage** | Generic error messages; detailed errors only in dev |
| **No request logging** | Added request logging middleware |
| **No 404 handling** | Added explicit 404 handler |

